VCS/Lite/Repository version 0.01
================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   VCS::Lite
   Algorithm::Diff
   YAML
   Time::Piece

